          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/162__step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/162__step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>apple cider vinegar</strong>, <strong>mayonnaise</strong> and the remaining <strong>chopped&nbsp;</strong><strong>tarragon</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>&nbsp;- this is your&nbsp;<strong>herby mayo</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season lightly with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Transfer the cooked, <strong>caramelised onions</strong> to a plate, reserving the pan for later</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
